{"tid":1491384,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我決定上tinder同香港警察約炮！！","createTime":"2019-08-20T11:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T16:29:59.000Z","uid":20948,"like":2292,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"c71c81226c965047c781bf1f813ab800f6d06783","tid":1491384,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"最近香港警察日日除暴安良，又冇時間陪老婆，仲要淪為過街老鼠，肯定好委屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有手足被CCTV影到斷送前途，肯定谷住條氣好需要發洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過日日揹幾十kg裝備跑黎跑去，本身唔fit都變fit啦，一諗起佢地成排朱古力，又可以無限氣續戰，小妹就覺得好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以！小妹決定上tinder約下啲警察出黎互相慰藉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n速龍優先，有份打甲由優先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果小妹有幸約到，肯定擺上黎曬命</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班暴徒就日日喺街疑神疑鬼，隨時俾人拉，我就搵警察哥哥仔用佢OT返黎嘅錢<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">開房</span></strong>玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放心到時約到邊間酒店我肯定話俾大家知，反正你班垃圾都係得把口，我就唔信你地真係夠膽玩<span style=\"color: red;\">麻包袋</span>，我敢講最多你地咪book我隔離房，偷聽我地翻雲覆雨然後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：藍絲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持小妹食警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人獸交不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8dfeb8afa555d04b341d82b7df2b6ebc8f5091","tid":1491384,"uid":20948,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:47:25.000Z","msg":